&lt;p&gt;If CI does not show any problems and the patch is approved I will push also JDK17 CI run.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;bq. This had to slip through when delivering&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
